01:06:31.860 --> 01:06:34.680
這就是殘酷的現實世界 安娜貝爾
This is the real world, Annabel.


716
01:06:36.740 --> 01:06:41.480
我們是在和一個叫伊斯蘭的國家中的激進分子作戰
We are fighting against the radical off cuts of a nation called Islam.


717
01:06:41.980 --> 01:06:43.610
你已經越過了界
You've crossed the line.


718
01:06:43.620 --> 01:06:46.120
你如今是站在他們一邊了
You're on their side now.


719
01:07:29.620 --> 01:07:30.850
你好
Hello.


720
01:07:41.980 --> 01:07:44.050
我不在乎你們打算怎麼對待我
I don't care what you do to me.


721
01:07:44.380 --> 01:07:47.720
可關鍵不在於你 不是嗎
But you're not the one we're talking about, are you, dear?


722
01:07:50.500 --> 01:07:53.040
伊薩 現在肯定很擔心
Issa must be worried sick.


723
01:07:53.780 --> 01:07:56.400
不管你把他藏在哪裡
Wherever you've hidden him,


724
01:07:56.980 --> 01:08:00.720
他恐怕在想你再也不會回去了
he's probably wondering if you're ever coming back.


725
01:08:06.660 --> 01:08:09.760
但願他不會做出傻事來
I hope he doesn't do anything foolish.


726
01:08:10.700 --> 01:08:12.850
來和我一起坐坐
Come, sit with me.


727
01:08:14.820 --> 01:08:16.560
來
Come on.


728
01:08:18.420 --> 01:08:22.050
現在有人想逮捕他
There are people out there who want to arrest him.


729
01:08:22.060 --> 01:08:24.450
當然你知道這事
You know that of course.


730
01:08:24.460 --> 01:08:28.320
我們擔心他們會在我們之前找到他
We're concerned that they will find him before we do.


731
01:08:28.660 --> 01:08:32.000
他們和我們的做事方式可大不一樣
There is a difference between them and us.


732
01:08:33.740 --> 01:08:36.120
他們想傷害他
They want to hurt him.


733
01:08:37.420 --> 01:08:39.720
我們想幫助他
We want to help him.


734
01:08:43.620 --> 01:08:46.570
安娜貝爾 我們不是你的敵人
You see, Annabel, we're not your enemy.


735
01:08:46.580 --> 01:08:48.840
而是你的出路
We're your solution.


736
01:09:08.940 --> 01:09:10.600
很好
Good.


737
01:09:52.500 --> 01:09:55.240
你知道我的人怎麼對我說的嗎
You know what my guys told me?


738
01:09:55.260 --> 01:09:58.280
當他們從街上抓走你的時候
When they pulled you off the street?


739
01:09:58.660 --> 01:10:01.200
你沒有做出反抗
You didn't put up a fight.


740
01:10:01.940 --> 01:10:03.800
沒像樣的反抗
Not really.


741
01:10:04.500 --> 01:10:05.610
只是稍稍掙扎了一下
You struggled a bit.


742
01:10:05.620 --> 01:10:07.880
喊了一下
Screamed a little, but


743
01:10:08.340 --> 01:10:10.760
就任由他們抓走你
you let them take you.


744
01:10:16.220 --> 01:10:19.920
似乎是你希望此事發生
It's almost as if you wanted it to happen.


745
01:10:22.020 --> 01:10:25.850
你需要有人接管此事
You needed someone to take it out of your hands


746
01:10:25.860 --> 01:10:29.280
因為你已經力所不及了 安娜貝爾
because you are out of your depth, Annabel.


747
01:10:33.100 --> 01:10:35.250
你知道你救不了他
You know you can't save him,


748
01:10:35.820 --> 01:10:37.920
至少靠你自己不行
not on your own.


749
01:10:43.380 --> 01:10:45.880
你要麼求助我們
Your choice is between us


750
01:10:46.820 --> 01:10:48.680
要麼找不到任何人
and nobody.


751
01:10:51.540 --> 01:10:53.880
時間已不多了
The clock is ticking.


752
01:10:56.700 --> 01:11:00.200
你知道他們會找到他 到時
You know they'll find him, and when they do,


753
01:11:00.700 --> 01:11:04.570
會立刻讓他坐飛機回俄國
he'll be on the first plane back to Russia,


754
01:11:04.580 --> 01:11:07.280
除非美國人想得到他
unless the Americans want him


755
01:11:07.420 --> 01:11:11.160
然後我們就不知道把他關在哪兒了 他也不會知道
and then we won't know where he is and nor will he.


756
01:11:13.180 --> 01:11:15.720
他不想要那筆錢
He doesn't want the money.


757
01:11:15.980 --> 01:11:18.440
就是不想要
He just doesn't want it.


758
01:11:22.140 --> 01:11:24.290
一半是激進分子 一半是
Half radical, half


759
01:11:25.340 --> 01:11:26.650
有錢的年輕人
rich kid.


760
01:11:26.660 --> 01:11:29.760
一半俄國人 一半車臣人
Half Russian, half Chechen.


761
01:11:30.580 --> 01:11:33.600
愛他母親 恨他父親
Loves his mother, hates his father.


762
01:11:33.700 --> 01:11:38.200
你我都清楚 伊薩•卡爾波夫並不知道自己想要什麼
You and I both know Issa Karpov has no idea what he wants.


763
01:11:40.700 --> 01:11:41.810
還有一點
There is something else


764
01:11:41.820 --> 01:11:44.600
是你我都知道的 是不是
you and I both know, don't we?


765
01:11:47.780 --> 01:11:50.600
我們都知道他是無辜的
We both know he's innocent.


766
01:12:04.900 --> 01:12:07.120
那麼你想幹什麼
So what do you want?


767
01:12:13.300 --> 01:12:15.520
我想幫他
I want to help him.


768
01:13:42.060 --> 01:13:43.680
伊薩
Issa?


769
01:13:54.700 --> 01:13:56.370
伊薩 對不起
Issa, I'm sorry.


770
01:13:56.380 --> 01:13:58.370
我做了個夢
I had a dream.


771
01:14:00.020 --> 01:14:02.920
他們抓走了你 拷打你
They took you. They tortured you.


772
01:14:11.740 --> 01:14:13.570
然後呢
And what happened?


773
01:14:16.540 --> 01:14:18.640
我告訴他們你在哪兒了嗎
Did I tell them where you were?


774
01:14:18.780 --> 01:14:20.170
沒有
No.


775
01:14:20.180 --> 01:14:22.210
你比我堅強
You are stronger than I was.


776
01:14:22.220 --> 01:14:24.600
你什麼都沒跟他們說
You tell them nothing.


777
01:14:26.340 --> 01:14:28.770
去穿些暖和的衣服
Go and put on something warm.


778
01:14:28.780 --> 01:14:31.280
我想帶你出去看看
I want to show you something outside.


779
01:16:22.460 --> 01:16:24.040
好
Okay.


780
01:16:30.180 --> 01:16:31.840
好
Right.


781
01:16:35.020 --> 01:16:36.930
看看他
Look at him.


782
01:16:38.260 --> 01:16:40.120
他很安全
He's safe.


783
01:16:41.900 --> 01:16:44.370
這裡還有你的床
There's a bed for you here.


784
01:16:44.380 --> 01:16:46.490
你最好別回家
It's better that you don't go home.


785
01:16:46.500 --> 01:16:49.120
穆爾先生和他的人還在找你
Herr Mohr and his boys are still out looking for you.


786
01:16:53.020 --> 01:16:55.770
你是想灌醉我嗎
Are you trying to get me drunk?


787
01:16:55.780 --> 01:16:57.400
是的
Yes.


788
01:16:58.260 --> 01:17:00.440
卡爾波夫怎麼樣了
How's Karpov?


789
01:17:00.500 --> 01:17:02.520
快了
Getting there.


790
01:17:03.060 --> 01:17:05.080
那律師呢
And the lawyer?


791
01:17:09.620 --> 01:17:12.880
我已經幫你儘量爭取了時間
I already got you all the time I can get.


792
01:17:16.900 --> 01:17:18.760
貝魯特的事兒是我們的錯
Beirut was our mistake.


793
01:17:20.100 --> 01:17:22.280
我們的一個特工
One of our agents


794
01:17:22.940 --> 01:17:26.880
毀了你的網絡 你分享了情報 是我們辦砸了
blew your network and I know you shared. We messed up.


795
01:17:28.460 --> 01:17:31.560
只想告訴你這一點
Just thought you needed to know that.


796
01:17:32.660 --> 01:17:35.360
我們經常犯類似錯誤
We make that kind of mistake.


797
01:17:38.020 --> 01:17:41.130
我能理解你為什麼信不過我們
I can understand why you don't trust us.


798
01:17:41.140 --> 01:17:44.640
你的特工和聯絡人暴露了
Your agents and contacts were compromised.


799
01:17:46.500 --> 01:17:49.810
一些信任你的人死了
Men who trusted you died,


800
01:17:49.820 --> 01:17:52.640
這會讓你永遠不能忘懷
and that stays with you always.


801
01:17:54.500 --> 01:17:56.680
我們留下的
And all that damage


802
01:17:57.700 --> 01:17:59.800
那些傷害
we leave behind.


803
01:18:07.300 --> 01:18:09.370
那些生命
All those lives,


804
01:18:11.180 --> 01:18:13.560
那些空蕩蕩的房子
all those empty rooms,


805
01:18:14.220 --> 01:18:16.960
他們本來的命運是什麼
what would they have been for?


806
01:18:18.260 --> 01:18:21.280
你問過自己這個問題嗎
You ever ask yourself that question?


807
01:18:23.020 --> 01:18:24.850
我們為何幹這行
Why we do what we do?


808
01:18:26.100 --> 01:18:27.850
有時也會問
Mmm-hmm, sometimes.


809
01:18:27.860 --> 01:18:29.970
可每次都是同樣的答案
But I always come back to the same answer.


810
01:18:29.980 --> 01:18:32.000
是什麼
And what is it?


811
01:18:33.060 --> 01:18:35.760
為了讓世界更安全
Make the world a safer place.


812
01:18:37.860 --> 01:18:39.520
這還不夠嗎
Isn't that enough?


813
01:19:10.060 --> 01:19:11.600
動一下你的皇后
Move your queen.


814
01:19:13.740 --> 01:19:15.210
雖然你是俄國人
Just because you're Russian,


815
01:19:15.220 --> 01:19:19.040
不等於你下棋比我強
doesn't mean you're a better chess player than me.


816
01:19:20.180 --> 01:19:22.090
我是車臣人
I'm Chechen.


817
01:19:22.420 --> 01:19:26.520
好吧 你下棋厲害
Okay, so you're good at chess.


818
01:19:27.220 --> 01:19:30.400
說說你別的方面
Tell me something else about yourself.


819
01:19:33.420 --> 01:19:36.240
你說過你母親是車臣人？
You said your mother is Chechen?


820
01:19:36.900 --> 01:19:38.400
她去世了
She's dead.


821
01:19:40.820 --> 01:19:42.680
對不起
I'm sorry.


822
01:19:44.420 --> 01:19:46.720
我父親強姦了她
My father raped her.


823
01:19:48.380 --> 01:19:50.410
她死於我出生那一天
She died when I was born.


824
01:19:55.020 --> 01:19:56.880
當時她15歲
She was 15.


825
01:20:06.260 --> 01:20:08.170
這是我媽媽的
It was my mother's.


826
01:20:11.620 --> 01:20:13.690
很漂亮
It's beautiful.


827
01:21:12.340 --> 01:21:14.280
你必須走
You must go.


828
01:21:41.380 --> 01:21:43.240
你可以再刺激一下他
You can push him a bit more.


829
01:21:44.260 --> 01:21:46.760
讓他動情緒
Try to get him emotional.


830
01:21:48.060 --> 01:21:51.400
只要是自然而然的 你不妨發發脾氣
If it happens naturally, lose your temper.


831
01:21:56.460 --> 01:21:58.730
可他不想要那筆錢
But he doesn't want the money.


832
01:21:58.740 --> 01:22:00.400
我知道
I know.


833
01:22:01.900 --> 01:22:04.080
可他喜歡你
But he wants you.


834
01:22:29.500 --> 01:22:31.090
昆特
Günther?


835
01:22:31.100 --> 01:22:32.810
你應該當心點
You should take care.


836
01:22:32.820 --> 01:22:35.520
也許我們太心急了
Maybe we're pushing too hard.


837
01:22:36.540 --> 01:22:39.080
你可別軟弱 伊娜
Don't go soft on me, Irna.


838
01:22:39.100 --> 01:22:41.440
在這件事上容不得軟弱
There's no room for that on this one.


839
01:22:42.620 --> 01:22:45.240
你哪件事上容許軟弱過？
Tell me one where there was.


840
01:23:08.100 --> 01:23:09.800
早上好
Morning.


841
01:23:24.060 --> 01:23:29.320
昨天有70人死於巴格達一處集市上
Seventy people died in a market in Baghdad yesterday.


842
01:23:39.580 --> 01:23:41.320
上帝的意旨
Insha Allah.


843
01:23:47.260 --> 01:23:49.120
"上帝的意旨"？
God's will?


844
01:23:49.340 --> 01:23:52.810
還是妄以上帝的名義來殺人？
Or just a man who was arrogant enough to kill in his name?


845
01:23:52.820 --> 01:23:54.440
她很厲害
She's good.


846
01:23:56.020 --> 01:23:59.000
萊拉和梅裡克都被逮捕了
Leyla and Melik have been arrested.


847
01:23:59.180 --> 01:24:01.530
他們可能會被驅逐出境
They may be deported,


848
01:24:01.540 --> 01:24:03.370
就因為他們對你好
because they were kind to you,


849
01:24:03.380 --> 01:24:05.880
因為他們把你請到家中
because they invited you in to their home.


850
01:24:07.180 --> 01:24:09.290
跟我解釋一下 伊薩
Explain it to me, Issa!


851
01:24:09.300 --> 01:24:11.210
上帝的意旨？
God's will?


852
01:24:11.340 --> 01:24:13.410
你解釋一下 那個在巴格達
Explain to me why that man who killed


853
01:24:13.420 --> 01:24:15.370
殺了那麼多婦女兒童的人
those women and children in Baghdad


854
01:24:15.380 --> 01:24:17.370
和你父親的行徑又有什麼不同
is any different from your own father?


855
01:24:17.380 --> 01:24:19.090
我來漢堡是為了開始新生活
I came to Hamburg to make a new life.


856
01:24:19.100 --> 01:24:22.850
不 你來漢堡是為了找湯姆•布魯先生
No. You came to Hamburg to find Mr. Tommy Brue.


857
01:24:22.860 --> 01:24:24.690
你來繼承你父親的錢
You came to claim your father's money.


858
01:24:24.700 --> 01:24:28.090
我跟你說過 我不想要他的錢
I told you, I do not want his money.


859
01:24:40.860 --> 01:24:42.720
原諒我
Forgive me.


860
01:24:58.900 --> 01:25:00.480
或許
Maybe


861
01:25:01.740 --> 01:25:07.000
有一個把過去拋在身後的辦法
there's a way to leave your past behind, Issa.


862
01:25:10.740 --> 01:25:13.090
-拿著你父親的錢   -拿著你父親的錢
- Take your father's money... - Take your father's money,


863
01:25:13.100 --> 01:25:17.280
-用它來做好事  -用它來做好事
- and turn it into something good. - ...and turn it into something good.


864
01:25:48.940 --> 01:25:51.320
你的山羊被拴住了
Your goat is tethered.


865
01:26:24.340 --> 01:26:26.530
只是一隻普通的筆
It's just an ordinary pen.


866
01:26:26.540 --> 01:26:30.760
看起來像是筆 寫起字也像 聽起來也像筆
Looks like a pen, writes like a pen and listens like a pen.


867
01:26:30.860 --> 01:26:33.450
拆開看依然是筆
Take it apart, it's still a pen.


868
01:26:33.460 --> 01:26:35.450
你明白了嗎
Are you clear?


869
01:26:35.500 --> 01:26:37.170
-明白啦  -嗯
- Are you clear? - Mmm-hmm.


870
01:26:37.180 --> 01:26:39.690
你是代表一個富有的穆斯林客戶
You are acting on behalf of a wealthy Muslim client.


871
01:26:39.700 --> 01:26:40.770
我們都談過了
We've been over this.


872
01:26:40.780 --> 01:26:42.170
你是代表一個富有的穆斯林客戶
You are acting on behalf of a wealthy Muslim...


873
01:26:42.180 --> 01:26:43.370
好幾次了
Several times.


874
01:26:43.380 --> 01:26:45.370
他來這裡繼承一大筆錢
...who has come in to a considerable inheritance


875
01:26:45.380 --> 01:26:47.650
而這筆錢的來路很可疑
and the source of the money is questionable.


876
01:26:47.660 --> 01:26:48.930
他想按照宗教精神
He seeks to distribute these funds


877
01:26:48.940 --> 01:26:50.130
捐獻出這筆錢
in a spiritually correct manner.


878
01:26:50.140 --> 01:26:52.320
真是的
For Christ's sake!


879
01:26:53.300 --> 01:26:56.200
我做這事不是為了你
I'm not doing this for you.


880
01:26:56.780 --> 01:26:59.040
不管是為了什麼 湯姆
Whatever it takes, Tommy.


881
01:27:56.660 --> 01:27:58.320
你好
Hello.


882
01:28:00.020 --> 01:28:01.720
抬起胳膊
Put your arms up.


883
01:28:06.100 --> 01:28:07.640
包
Bag?


884
01:28:20.940 --> 01:28:22.170
嗨
Hi.


885
01:28:24.300 --> 01:28:25.410
-嗨  -你好
- Hi. - Hello.


886
01:28:25.420 --> 01:28:26.490
-布魯先生嗎  -是的
- Mr. Brue? - Yes.


887
01:28:26.500 --> 01:28:27.610
-歡迎  -謝謝
- Welcome. - Thank you.


888
01:28:27.620 --> 01:28:28.690
我是賈馬爾
I'm Jamal.


889
01:28:28.700 --> 01:28:30.090
我父親在等你
My father is expecting you.


890
01:28:30.100 --> 01:28:31.890
-你能脫了鞋嗎  -好的
- Can you take off your shoes? - Of course.


891
01:28:31.900 --> 01:28:34.120
大衣交給我吧
I'll take care of the coat.


892
01:28:40.940 --> 01:28:42.450
布魯先生
Mr. Brue.


893
01:28:42.460 --> 01:28:44.720
-布魯先生  -幸會
- Mr. Brue. - An honor.


894
01:28:49.820 --> 01:28:51.290
你見過我兒子賈馬爾了吧
You have met my son Jamal?


895
01:28:51.300 --> 01:28:54.720
是的還有門外的一個人
Yes, and, uh, another at the door, I believe.


896
01:28:55.380 --> 01:28:57.290
請坐
Please sit.


897
01:29:02.020 --> 01:29:03.720
請
Please.


898
01:29:07.460 --> 01:29:09.170
正像我跟你解釋過的
As explained to you,


